OL,7,FForensic accountants will investigate
OL,8,Fwhy NI Water is unlikely to stay
OL,9,Fwithin its budget at a time that
OL,10,F"difficult decisions are having to be
OL,11,Fmade across all Executive departments
OL,12,Fand arm's-length bodies," the
OL,13,FInfrastructure Minister has said.
OL,15,FLiz Kimmins told the Northern Ireland
OL,16,FAssembly she had made the decision
OL,17,Fafter being informed by the board of
OL,18,FNI Water that the company could
OL,19,Foverspend by #3million.
