OL,7,FThe minister said she had to
OL,8,F"investigate the reasons why NI Water
OL,9,Fhas been unable to live within its
OL,10,Fresource budget allocation".
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Water, which is
OL,13,Ffunded by the Department for
OL,14,FInfrastructure, provides water and
OL,15,Fsewerage services.
OL,17,FIt has previously warned that
OL,18,Funcertainty of financial support and
OL,19,Fhistoric underfunding are having a
OL,20,Fserious impact on services.
