OL,3,CForensic accountants to examine NI
OL,4,CWater budget as overspend warning
OL,5,Cissued
OL,7,F"During the year, recognising the
OL,8,Fimportance of water and wastewater
OL,9,Fservices, bids for additional funding
OL,10,Ffor NI Water were submitted as part of
OL,11,Fthe in-year monitoring process.
OL,13,F"An additional #11.5million resource
OL,14,Fwas secured for NI Water in-year.
OL,16,F"In addition, #2.9m was also provided
OL,17,Fto deal with the aftermath of Storm
OL,18,FEowyn, bringing the current allocation
OL,19,Fto just over #152m .
