OL,3,CForensic accountants to examine NI
OL,4,CWater budget as overspend warning
OL,5,Cissued
OL,7,F"It was made clear to NI Water that it
OL,8,Fwas required to live within the
OL,9,Fincreased resource allocation as it
OL,10,Fwas unlikely that any further funding
OL,11,Fwould become available.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, in recent weeks, the
OL,14,Fboard of NI Water has indicated in
OL,15,Fwriting that it is minded to instruct
OL,16,FNI Water to overspend unless
OL,17,Fadditional budget is available.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
