OL,3,CForensic accountants to examine NI
OL,4,CWater budget as overspend warning
OL,5,Cissued
OL,7,F"It is estimated that any potential
OL,8,Foverspend could be in the region of
OL,9,F#3m, although the exact quantum of
OL,10,Fthis remains subject to cost
OL,11,Fvariations between now and year-end
OL,12,Fclose."
OL,14,FShe added: "It is essential I fully
OL,15,Funderstand the budgetary management
OL,16,Fdecisions that NI Water have taken
OL,17,Fthis year that have led to the board
OL,18,Fof NI Water proposing this
OL,19,Funprecedented and disappointing course
OL,20,Fof action."
